spec_data.Name: php-phpseclib-crypt-hash
spec_data.Description:
Uses hash() or mhash() if available and an internal implementation,
otherwise.  Optionally uses suhosin. Currently supports the following:
md2, md5, md5-96, sha1, sha1-96, sha256, sha384, and sha512.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:54:27 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Pure-PHP implementations of keyed HMACs and hashing functions
